                <h1>"Does a 302 Appear on Background Checks?"</h1>
                <p>A 302 will typically not show up on a standard background check since it's a civil commitment and not a criminal charge. However, comprehensive background checks can sometimes reveal mental health commitments. It's important to check specific state laws and the type of background check being conducted.</p>
